&lt;p&gt;Easthampstead Surgery is a warm friendly practice serving a population of 5000 patients. We are seeking a  PRACTICE NURSE, to provide and maintain a high standard of nursing care for patients as well as providing nursing assistance to doctors. The Practice Nurse will deliver evidence-based care for patients presenting with long term conditions and provide preventative health care to the practice population.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You should have years of experience working in General Practice and should be able to do chronic disease reviews with  QOF.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal visits welcome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary: Best in the industry for the right candidate.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job Type: Full time Permanent&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours: Minimum 30 hours per week if not working on Thursday.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Start: ASAP&lt;/p&gt;
